snippet.textDisplay:
When you have been taught that the earth is a spinning globe flying through space your entire life, the idea of the earth being flat sounds erroneous. But i decided to do my own research on the model of the earth and what views is accepted today.
1st: According to the Encyclopedia Britannica the "Geocentric modelof the earth is , any theory of the structure of the solar system (or the universe) in which Earth is assumed to be at the center of it all. The most highly developed geocentric model was that of Ptolemy of Alexandria (2nd century CE). It was generally accepted until the 16th century, after which it was superseded by heliocentric models such as that of Nicolaus Copernicus. Compare heliocentrism; Ptolemaic system; Tychonic system."


2nd: According to the Encyclopedia Britannica the helicentric model of the earth is "Heliocentrism,is a cosmological model in which the Sun is assumed to lie at or near a central point (e.g., of the solar system or of the universe) while the Earth and other bodies revolve around it. In the 5th century BC the Greek philosophers Philolaus and Hicetas speculated separately that the Earth was a sphere revolving daily around some mystical “central fire” that regulated the universe. Two centuries later, Aristarchus of Samos extended this idea by proposing that the Earth and other planets moved around a definite central object, which he believed to be the Sun."


My opinion /view: I believe in the Geocentric model of the earth is because according to Chronicles @: "He has fixed the earth firm, immovable." and the reason why I believe that we have not been out of space because God created the firmament which nothing can penetrate. the sun and the moon is inside the firmament and it rotates around the earth. The bible says the there are lights in the firmament that he will have for signs and for season according to (Genesis 1: 14-17) And God said, Let there be lights in the firmament of the heaven to divide the day from the night; and let them be for signs, and for seasons, and for days, and years:
And let them be for lights in the firmament of the heaven to give light upon the earth: and it was so. And God made two great lights; the greater light to rule the day, and the lesser light to rule the night: he made the stars also. My hearts goes out to Mad Mike Hughes and his passion for what he was doing; my prayers goes out to his family as well. Other than that if you have read this post this is where I stand and I want t thank you for the time for reading this. For anyone who do not have a relationship with Jesus Christ and if you was to leave this earth today and not know if you would make it into heaven or not I need you to repeat this prayer with me that if you confess with your mouth the Lord Jesus and believe in your heart that God has raised Him from the dead, you will be saved. For with the heart one believes unto righteousness, and with the mouth confession is made unto salvation (Romans10:9). If you have sincerely said this prayer you have been saved from God's wrath against sinners and you will be saved from hell and Jesus will accept you into his kingdom because you have repented and said yes to him. God bless!
